reviews.text:
Well known Taiwanese tea house. It is a small sized and only for taking out.

People were very nice and tried their best to make us understand what they are selling.

Tea were well designed and prepared. I tried bubble tea and ginger tea. Bubble tea offers a good balance between tea flavor and milk. They use fresh milk. Ginger tea tasted rich and deep. Very good before on board especially when you feel not good. The both were much higher quality than any other brands in the town.
Perfect! A nice cup of brown sugar pearl milk tea at a great location. Such a beautiful view can be found less than 50m away! Staff is very friendly & helpful.
Best bubble cup tea I've ever had! 10/10!
Refreshing fruit tea - will definitely go back again 👍
水果茶中的糖份同樣是減肥致命傷！參考一芳水果茶台灣網站提供的糖份比例，一杯全糖的水果茶足足有17茶匙的糖份，即使是最少的微微糖也有一茶匙糖在內。
